  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "Riley Centrella built this herself in 3060, the first upgrade she ever worked on before Firefly Foundry even existed. Stripped the Hammerhands down and replaced everything. Twin Ultra AC/10s, Streak SRM 6, ER lasers, double heat sinks. She piloted it through operations on Carmichael, Palm and Novo Tressida until 3079 when Word of Blake's Shadow Division finally cornered her on Ur Cruinne. She lured them into an oil refinery and took them all out with her. This mech went with her. What you have in the bay is something that should not exist.",
